<task id="task-7153" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Set the default selection method</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">To set the default selection method used in the Spy/Recorder of a project, do as follows:</context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Open Katalon Studio, then go to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Project</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Settings</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Test Design</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Web UI</uicontrol>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="700" href="image/ks-855-web-test-design.png" class="- topic/image "/></info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">For Katalon Studio version 7.6.0 backward, go to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Project</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Settings</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Test Design</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Web Locators</uicontrol>.</info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Under the line <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Default element locator value of test objects generated by Recorder or Spy</uicontrol>, select one of these provided options:</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="xpath.dita" class="- topic/xref ">XPath</xref>: Once a test object is captured using Spy/Recorder, a set of XPath locators is generated. The first value is the object's default XPath locator.</li><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="attributes.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Attributes</xref></li><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="css.dita" class="- topic/xref ">CSS</xref></li><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="image.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Image</xref></li></ul></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">If you choose XPath or Attributes, you need to configure additional settings. To learn more, see below:</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="configure_xpath.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Configure XPath</xref>.</li><li class="- topic/li "><xref href="configure_attributes.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Configure Attributes</xref>.</li></ul></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">When you are done, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Apply and Close</uicontrol>.</cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>